# Cursor Rule: Docs Design Workflow

- Use `docs/<topic>/design.md` for the design and `docs/<topic>/tasks.md` for
  execution tracking.

- Reference the design doc explicitly at the top of `tasks.md`.

- Use `- [ ]` and `- [x]` in `tasks.md`, and keep the checklist current as
  work progresses.

- If a design changes implementation expectations, update the nearest
  `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, and compatibility instruction files when they
  become stale.
